Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Lists Are Ubiquitous in Wolfram Language", "Subsection",ExpressionUUID->"05ac3717-0399-46c0-ac66-6e2d6114f935"],

Cell["\<\
Lists also play a special role as part of Wolfram Language syntax for many \
built-in functions. In most cases, lists are used to specify \
variables/iterators and their bounds.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"a01651dc-e7bf-4916-a6dd-ba4e7fb8b7b2"],

